      Aero
    </div>
    <div class="convo-divider"></div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="convo-heading convo-reveal">
    The problem nobody talks about<span class="convo-cursor"></span>
  </h2>

  <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
    Every conversation with AI starts from zero. Your frameworks, patterns, refined language — gone when the chat window closes.
  </p>

  <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
    We call it <strong>AI Amnesia</strong>: the most expensive problem nobody names.
  </p>

  <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
    Your intellectual property isn't just what you've published. It's <em>the thinking between the thinking</em> — the connections you make, the models you've built, the instincts you've honed. All of it evaporates between sessions.
  </p>

  <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
    We built Multiplist Studios to solve this. Not with better prompts. With an entirely new architecture.
  </p>
</div>

